      "identifier": "ea:concept:voice-technology",
      "name": "Voice Technology",
      "abstract": "Voice technology spans recording, metadata, speech interfaces, voice archives, speech datasets and machine listening without reducing voice to a model output.",
      "description": "Voice technology is the design and engineering of systems that capture, analyze, transform, preserve or present spoken voice as technical and cultural material.",
